f1 = NamedTemporaryFile('wt', delete=False)
try:
    f1.write('fofo')
    f1.close()
    f2 = NamedTemporaryFile('wt', delete=False)
    try:
        f2.write('fofo')
        f2.close()
        self.assertTrue(same_content(f1.name, f2.name))
    finally:
        os.remove(f2.name)
finally:
    os.remove(f1.name)
